    "about": "Uniswap V4 is an automated market maker protocol introducing customizable and extensible liquidity pools via hooks. The singleton PoolManager architecture consolidates all pool state and logic in a single contract per chain, enabling gas-efficient multi-hop swaps. Users provide liquidity as non-fungible positions managed by the permissionless PositionManager, supporting dynamic fee tiers and custom hook implementations. The protocol uses flash accounting with transient storage to defer balance settlement until transaction completion."
